                }
            },
            "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
            "body": "question: can dir_len be 0? we could consider changing this to\n```\n-      char *p = &dir_name[dir_len - 1];\n-      while (dir_len > 1 && vim_ispathsep(*p)) {\n-        *p-- = NUL;\n-        dir_len--;\n+      while (dir_len > 1 && vim_ispathsep(dir_name[dir_len - 1])) {\n+        dir_name[--dir_len] = NUL;\n       }\n```",
